text: First time visit this shop recommended by my customer. Place was clean, masseuse Anna was good too. Staff did not hard sell any package. Their promotion are good, check with the shop directly :)
Had a tuina session with Yoyo for an hour, it was an amazing time. Felt so relaxed! Will definitely go back for gua sha and cupping!

I went in with back pain, and the therapist took the time to understand my condition before starting treatment. Focused entirely on the affected area and used guasha, cupping, and tuina techniques. The treatment was targeted and professional, and I could feel the difference afterward. Highly recommended for anyone dealing with muscle tension or back pain.
MDM TCM environment is clean and with nice touch of Chinese element renovation. The vibe is comfortable and relaxing.  Annaâ€™s massaging skill is good, right on the spot. Highlight recommended.

Yo Yo, is very experienced & detailed therapist. After the session I felt rejuvenated. No regrets to have her massage for me.
Nice & calming environment which is what I like. I often fall asleep during the session as it's very comfortable.
